---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import service from "../assets/service.png";
import service2 from "../assets/service2.png";
import service3 from "../assets/service3.png";
---

<section id="services" class="py-16 bg-blue-200 w-screen">
  <div class="container max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-gray-500 md:px-12 xl:px-0">
    <div class="mx-auto grid gap-6 md:w-3/4 lg:w-full lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl px-8 py-12 sm:px-12 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mb-12 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-900">Quality</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Graphene Nano-Tech is a revolutionary process infusing graphene into every Aqua Technics pool. Graphene is the strongest material known to man and we have incorporated this nano-material to create our strongest pool ever built. 
          </p>
          <a href="/graphene-nano-technology" class="block font-medium text-blue-600">Know more</a>
        </div>
        <Image
          src={service}
          class="w-2/3 ml-auto -mb-12"
          alt="illustration"
          format="webp"
          loading="lazy"
          width="900"
          height="600"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl px-8 py-12 sm:px-12 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mb-12 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-900">Colors</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            The ColorGuard pools range of colors will maintain their beautiful appearance and vivid color for many years.

            The most popular colors by far, they suit any of our pool designs and look amazing day or night.
          </p>
          <a href="/colors" class="block font-medium text-blue-600">Know more</a>
        </div>
        <Image
          src={service2}
          class="w-2/3 ml-auto"
          alt="illustration"
          format="webp"
          loading="lazy"
          width="900"
          height="600"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl px-8 py-12 sm:px-12 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mb-12 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-900">Pools</h3>
          <p class="mb-6">
            The very best fiberglass pool available anywhere in the world.
          </p>
          <a href="/pools" class="block font-medium text-blue-600">Know more</a>
        </div>
        <Image
          src={service3}
          class="w-2/3 ml-auto"
          format="webp"
          alt="illustration"
          loading="lazy"
          width="900"
          height="600"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
